{
  "stem": "11801.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The, the television and the media, you know, sort of has homogenized so many societies, so many countries, that to move or to, to travel, you know, the language may pose a problem, but the way of life is not that different.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "At that time, coming to the United States from Belgium was like coming from a-- I often compare it-- from a Victorian society into the late 20th century.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "That's how I saw it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We finally got on this ship, which took two weeks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it was a very rough passage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And, in any case, I was very nervous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I, I didn't mind leaving the orphanage, although I did wonder-- I mean, I was very excited about coming to the United States, like everyone else in Europe.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "At that time, the United States-- there was nothing like it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You know, it was the country to be in and the place where you would find-- where your dreams would come true.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we were very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We knew that, that we had the opportunity to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My, my father had sent me some clothes, as I mentioned earlier.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And one of the items that he had sent me was a red Chesterfield coat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It was a coat with a black velvet collar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I'll always remember it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And as the ship was approaching New York, my mother told me to put on my coat, which I really resented.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know, again, I was sort of being singled out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I was being-- I don't know, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I knew, of course, why I had to do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I hadn't seen my father in almost eight years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I certainly was not the same child.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
